_sText:
This map made by me, RoteXoR. There are four levels where each is harder than the last one. The more levels you complete, the better gun you get when time's up.

If you manage to complete level four, you get an m249, and everyone else will only get a knife. You will also be teleported to a higher level in the jail, so you don't risk getting killed by all the people with knives.
